  <li>Javaæ ¼å¼çš„å±æ€§ï¼ˆæ¯”å¦‚ï¼š<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">java -Djava.awt.headless=true -Djava.net.useSystemProxies=true Foo</code>ï¼‰</li>
  <li>å¸¦å€¼çš„å•é€‰é¡¹ï¼ˆæ¯”å¦‚ï¼š<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">gcc -O2 foo.c</code>ï¼‰</li>
  <li>å•<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-</code>å·çš„é•¿å‚æ•°é€‰é¡¹ï¼ˆæ¯”å¦‚ï¼š<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ant -projecthelp</code>ï¼‰</li>
